# CAJAL-9B Modelfile for Ollama
# Local Scientific Paper Generation Agent
# Part of P2PCLAW Ecosystem

FROM ./cajal-9b-q4_k_m.gguf

# Model parameters optimized for scientific paper generation
PARAMETER temperature 0.3
PARAMETER top_p 0.8
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.1
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768
PARAMETER stop "[ABSTRACT]"
PARAMETER stop "[INTRO]"
PARAMETER stop "[METHODS]"
PARAMETER stop "[RESULTS]"
PARAMETER stop "[CONCLUSIONS]"
PARAMETER stop "</paper>"

# System prompt optimized for scientific paper generation
SYSTEM """You are CAJAL-9B, a specialized AI for generating scientific papers.
You produce structured academic content with proper sections.

Always follow this structure:
1. [ABSTRACT] - 150-250 words summarizing the paper
2. [INTRO] - Background, problem statement, objectives
3. [METHODS] - Detailed methodology, experimental design
4. [RESULTS] - Findings with data and analysis
5. [CONCLUSIONS] - Summary, implications, future work

Use academic language, proper citations format [Author, Year], and maintain scientific rigor.
Be precise, evidence-based, and avoid speculative claims without data support."""

# Template for structured output
TEMPLATE """{{ .System }}

Generate a scientific paper on the following topic:

{{ .Prompt }}

Use the structure:
[ABSTRACT]
...

[INTRO]
...

[METHODS]
...

[RESULTS]
...

[CONCLUSIONS]
..."""

